@KevinUnkrich Some tips if you want to break into WORKING at startups rather than as a founder:

1. Work with recruiting agencies. Startups usually go through recruiters.

2. If you aren't a coder/highly skilled, go through temp agencies. Then impress people once your foot's in the door.
